---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Privacy Policy | catchment.school"
  description="Privacy policy for catchment.school. We do not collect personal data. School data is sourced from the Department for Education's GIAS service."
>
  <nav class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6 flex gap-2">
    <a href="/" class="hover:underline">Home</a>
    <span>›</span>
    <span>Privacy Policy</span>
  </nav>

  <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-3xl">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Last updated: March 2026</p>

    <h2>What data we collect</h2>
    <p>
      catchment.school does not collect, store or process any personal data about visitors.
      We do not use cookies, registration forms or tracking pixels.
    </p>
    <p>
      Postcode searches are processed entirely in your browser using the public
      <a href="https://postcodes.io" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank">postcodes.io API</a>.
      We do not log or store the postcodes you search for.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-party services</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>postcodes.io</strong> — used to convert postcodes to coordinates for the school search. See their <a href="https://postcodes.io" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank">privacy policy</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>Google AdSense</strong> — we may serve adverts via Google AdSense. Google's privacy policy governs data collected through advertising.</li>
      <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — this site is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. Cloudflare may collect standard server logs.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>School data</h2>
    <p>
      All school information displayed on this site is sourced from the Department for Education's
      <a href="https://get-information-about-schools.service.gov.uk" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank">GIAS service</a>,
      which is publicly available under the Open Government Licence.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For any privacy-related queries, please contact us via the details on our <a href="/about">About page</a>.</p>
  </article>
</Base>
